description:
Drake Jaden returns to Naked Kombat to break his even record of 1-1. This ripped stud has been doing cardio to prepare for the match. His opponent this time around is Tucker Forrest, a bad boy with tattoos and a Prince Albert. Tucker plans to fuck Drake with his PA when he wins. This is Tucker first time on NK and Drake is using this to his full advantage. Has Tucker done his homework and read the rules on NK?
The NK Rules are in the menu above.
title: Drake Jaden vs. Tucker Forrest
